{"tid":767919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐洲熱浪致大麥失收影響啤酒業","createTime":"2018-08-05T03:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T09:34:45.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a549695eda8c05d9729889668e98ce255d0c4cb8","tid":767919,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"歐洲熱浪致大麥失收影響啤酒業<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=315361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D315361&d=OF85xTxwdB8Jrd18ODRdZ1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=1168b978\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D315361&h=1858a36e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=315361</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】歐洲在熱浪侵襲下，大麥產量下跌。由於大麥是釀製啤酒原料之一，令歐洲多間啤酒廠面臨無法生產的問題。<br />\n<br />\n熱浪席捲歐洲多國，不少地方的溫度紀錄持續創新高，除了一般民眾叫苦，農民因為多款農作物因酷熱失收而深受其害。<br />\n<br />\n在部分歐洲國家，大麥的產量下跌近五成，業界甚至預測今年大麥產量將減少50萬噸。事件導致歐洲大麥的價格自五月起急升近三分之二，高見230歐元一噸。<br />\n<br />\n由於大麥是啤酒主要材料，大麥失收令歐洲啤酒業界面對成本上漲及原料短缺的問題，有分析員表示，情況可以用「可怕」來形容。<br />\n<br />\n今年歐洲啤酒業已經要面對食用級二氧化碳短缺問題，部分英國啤酒品牌更因此而停產，現時再加上大麥供應緊張，將令啤酒業再受打擊。<br />\n<br />\n不過即使啤酒廠有足夠原料生產啤酒，也仍要面對如何送到消費者手上的問題。<br />\n<br />\n在德國，由於今年夏天天氣炎熱，不少民眾選擇飲啤酒消暑，雖然令啤酒銷售量上升，但啤酒廠同時出現玻璃瓶數量不足的情形。有啤酒廠甚至公開呼籲顧客快點將啤酒瓶退回，以免廠方無酒可賣。"},{"pid":"4b919eac909e0e61aced0acd5e922e29fcadb96a","tid":767919,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:36:39.000Z","msg":"不嬲飲開日本啤"},{"pid":"3a05a0f461eebbeefe0b92bbc3a66e3e519eba30","tid":767919,"uid":41245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4b919eac909e0e61aced0acd5e922e29fcadb96a","tid":767919,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:36:39.000Z","msg":"不嬲飲開日本啤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:56:24.000Z","msg":"好犀利呀"},{"pid":"b69094591935f1d259214d62c41f9fef29c0b472","tid":767919,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:59:33.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"140eebd99ca4dd50f715f85ac3f66f06f0202fd5","tid":767919,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:10:50.000Z","msg":"叫香港送D過去囉，香港啲玻璃直接倒入堆填區"},{"pid":"bb51d4d967a4a71d0dacdfefb03d0e2bcc597de4","tid":767919,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T04:53:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得熱浪幾好食"},{"pid":"6419959ffb1e19f5591b2b0a8df87cadd4f9744d","tid":767919,"uid":173494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/05/141014_c5cc53dbc79a340f02704f712160663a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F05%2F141014_c5cc53dbc79a340f02704f712160663a.png&h=a4a587cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"914ba05c0ef44222c6c483105430ba41eda51318","tid":767919,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T08:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b66a2aa606c3870a2101ffc02efd12b74652dc","tid":767919,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T09:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲飲開青島啤</blockquote>"}]}